The paper discusses the task of image captioning, which involves both image processing and natural language processing. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of deep neural architectures, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the model using standard evaluation matrices, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
